--- INSTRUCTIONS ---
Produce your analysis as structured JSON matching the output schema. Focus specifically on:
1. OT/ICS-specific attack patterns — not generic IT threats
2. Energy sector targeting — power grids, oil & gas, pipelines, utilities
3. ICS Cyber Kill Chain stages alongside MITRE ATT&CK for ICS
4. Physical consequence potential (operational disruption, safety risk)
5. OT protocol exploitation (Modbus, DNP3, OPC-UA, S7Comm, EtherNet/IP)
